subsetsum

Class Sublist<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • subsetsum.Sublist<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    class Sublist<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Sublist class can represents any subset of given set, S, and it can generate new subset from existing subsets. Sublist stores indices references from master set, from which are formed subsets.
    Author:
    Foothill College, Veronika Cabalova Joseph
